17/03/2011
PODGORICA, Montenegro -- Montenegro's and Serbia's future lies within the EU, President Filip Vujanovic said on Wednesday (March 16th) at the opening of Serbia's consulate in Herceg Novi. 
He said the diplomatic office represents another bridge between the two countries. 
Serbian President Boris Tadic said that Belgrade and Montenegro should use all potential for mutual co-operation in the region before joining the EU. 
(RTS, Portal Analitika, Mina - 16/03/11)
